msgstr "%s on tundmatu Windows rakendusi."

#: .././bin/mint-exec-guard-windows:69
msgid "Some Windows apps may not be compatible with Windows App Support."
msgstr "Mõned Windowsi rakendused ei pruugi ühilduda Windows App tugi."

